<view class="c13-drawer-page c13-step-two">
  <view class="c13-bg-report">
    <view class="c13-status"><text>9:41</text><text>wifi</text></view>
    <view class="c13-bg-top">
      <button bindtap="onTap" data-action="back">‹</button>
      <text>完整报告</text>
      <text>错题 1 / 8</text>
    </view>
    <text class="c13-bg-title">AI 提分报告（完整）</text>
    <text class="c13-bg-time">报告生成时间：2024-05-30 10:36</text>
    <image class="c13-bg-owl c13-pointer-owl" src="/assets/icons/owl-teacher-pointer.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <view class="c13-bg-score full">
      <view class="c13-score-row">
        <image class="c13-score-icon" src="/assets/clean-icons/shield-check-purple.png" mode="aspectFit" />
        <view><text>可追回分数</text><text class="c13-score-sub">可优先改善</text></view>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-score-value"><text>6-10</text><text>分</text><text>↑</text></view>
      <text class="c13-score-note">通过优先修复关键错因，有机会追回的分数区间</text>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="c13-overlay dark"></view>

  <view class="c13-drawer">
    <view class="c13-handle"></view>
    <view class="c13-drawer-head">
      <text>修复这道关键错题</text>
      <button bindtap="onTap" data-action="back">×</button>
    </view>
    <view class="c13-progress">
      <view class="c13-line active-two"></view>
      <view class="c13-step done"><text>1</text><text>错因诊断</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step active"><text>2</text><text>换法讲解</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step"><text>3</text><text>验证练习</text></view>
      <view class="c13-step"><text>4</text><text>掌握判断</text></view>
    </view>
    <scroll-view class="c13-drawer-scroll" scroll-y="true" enhanced="true" show-scrollbar="false">
      <view class="c13-panel">
        <text class="c13-panel-title">错题 1 二元一次方程应用题</text>
        <view class="c13-answer-table three">
          <text>学生答案</text><text>正确答案</text><text>错因依据</text>
          <text>20 千米</text><text>45 千米</text><text>速度差 × 时间计算错误</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="c13-panel c13-teach">
        <text class="c13-panel-title">换一种方式讲</text>
        <text>关键是把“甲比乙多行”理解为：路程差。每小时相差 10 千米，2 小时就是 20 千米。</text>
        <view class="c13-method-card">
          <image class="c13-method-icon" src="/assets/icons/idea-bulb-soft.png" mode="aspectFit" />
          <text>更容易理解的讲法</text>
          <text>把两辆车想象成一直在并排走，甲每小时多走 10 千米，2 小时后，甲就比乙多走了 2 × 10 = 20（千米）。</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <button class="c13-primary" bindtap="onTap" data-action="exercise">下一步：做 1 道验证题</button>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>
</view>
